docstrings: * **REQUIRED**. This string MUST be the {@link https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html semantic version number} of the {@link https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/blob/main/versions/3.0.3.md#versions OpenAPI Specification version} that the OpenAPI document uses. The `openapi` field SHOULD be used by tooling specifications and clients to interpret the OpenAPI document. This is _not_ related to the API {@link https://github.com/OAI/OpenAPI-Specification/blob/main/versions/3.0.3.md#infoVersion `info.version`} string.
